get="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7adab3a829b0b0c8ede37974d2601-kix.9ddoym69rymf-1024x575.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7adab3a829b0b0c8ede37974d2601-kix.9ddoym69rymf-1024x575.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7adab3a829b0b0c8ede37974d2601-kix.9ddoym69rymf-300x168.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7adab3a829b0b0c8ede37974d2601-kix.9ddoym69rymf-768x431.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7adab3a829b0b0c8ede37974d2601-kix.9ddoym69rymf-jpg.webp 1137w" width="1024" height="575" /></a></p><p> MV中的动画质量简直令人惊叹。门卷流畅的舞蹈、让众多舞者和观众兴奋不已的表情、作为骗子的独特表情、酷炫的说唱部分、最后激动人心的轮目。内容充满了高标准的一切，使其成为您一刻都无法移开视线的视频。</p><h2> [原创]波浪声的前奏/Mashiro Nagino[动画MV] </h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[原创]波浪声的前奏/Mashiro Nagino[动画MV]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/h1Fc7D5wdrU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@naginomashiro" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>懋野真白</strong></a>上传的原创新MV是一部以大海的蓝色、天空的蓝色以及懋野真白的歌声清澈透明的蓝色为特色的作品。动画部分较多，摄影作品也有速度感，所以当你走向歌曲的后半部分时，视频会给你一种愉快的自由感。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7adab3a829b0b0c8ede37974d2601-kix.gvk3ig7bmxbf-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7adab3a829b0b0c8ede37974d2601-kix.gvk3ig7bmxbf-1024x571.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7adab3a829b0b0c8ede37974d2601-kix.gvk3ig7bmxbf-1024x571.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7adab3a829b0b0c8ede37974d2601-kix.gvk3ig7bmxbf-300x167.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2018/01/83a7a